source.name: Oregon State Marine Board's Boating Regulations Handbook 2011-2013
source.description: Learn the rules and regulations for operating motorboats on Oregon's waterways. This handbook contains waterway-specific rules, equipment requirements, and navigation "rules of the road." It can be printed and folded vertically for easy storage in your boat compartment.
